					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13141045#post-4544711</guid>
				<title>Pizza Time</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13141045/scp-5522#post-4544711</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2020 22:40:21 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Deadly Bread</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3988532</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="text-align: center;"> <blockquote> <p><span style="font-size:110%;">Player [Deadly Bread] has left the game: [VAC Banned from SCP Foundation]</span></p> </blockquote> </div> <hr /> <p>My entry to Jamcon Day Two. This started as a joke about jumping in a pizzeria to glitch into the floor and get the food delivered on time. Now its this. Also most of these glitches were pulled from my experience speedrunning Half-Life 2, hence the name Λ-Events.</p> <p>Huge thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/justbixby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5272357&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584973610" alt="JustBixby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5272357)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/justbixby" >JustBixby</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/laneous" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4894577&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584973610" alt="Laneous" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4894577)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/laneous" >Laneous</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/westrin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2858989&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584973610" alt="Westrin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2858989)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/westrin" >Westrin</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jakdragonx" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5588260&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584973610" alt="JakdragonX" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5588260)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jakdragonx" >JakdragonX</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/henzoid" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5190300&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584973610" alt="Henzoid" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5190300)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/henzoid" >Henzoid</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xilascrowe" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2969291&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584973610" alt="XilasCrowe" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2969291)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xilascrowe" >XilasCrowe</a></span> for each giving this a read and providing some very helpful feedback.</p> <p>No images yet, but maybe once Jamcon is officially over.</p> <hr /> <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/the-bread-box">Other Articles of Mine</a></p> </div> 
				 	]]>
